commit.message:
Makefile.am (cond_gtk_gcjawt_ltlibrary): Rename libjawt.la libgcjawt.la.

2005-05-12  Thomas Fitzsimmons  <fitzsim@redhat.com>

	* Makefile.am (cond_gtk_gcjawt_ltlibrary): Rename libjawt.la
	libgcjawt.la.

From-SVN: r99636

+
